title: Win.Xp.Sp2-Key.Generator
description:
Generate a 640 Product Key for WinXP Pro Corporate Editions with Service Pack 2.
The Windows update v5 via web works fine!

Greetz
Sandman2000

- start keygen.exe
- change product family to &quot;Windows XP Pro VLK&quot;
- Hit &quot;Generate&quot; as many times you like, and pick your unique license key ;-)

- start C:/windows/system32/oobe.exe
- select order by phone
- hit next
- hit change product key
- enter new key
- close window
- you're done!
